1. *Razgovaraj* s njim i pokušaj da razumeš njegove probleme. (Talk* to him and try to understand his problems.)
2. Oni *razgovaraju* već sat vremena. (They have been *talking* for an hour.)
3. Molim te, ne mogu sada *razgovarati*, javit ću ti se kasnije. (Please, I can't *talk* now, I will get back to you later.)
4. Kada *razgovaram* s tobom, uvijek se osjećam bolje. (When I *talk* to you, I always feel better.)
5. Da li ti i tvoj partner *razgovarate* o budućnosti? (Do you and your partner *talk* about the future?)
6. Naš šef uvijek nam daje priliku da *razgovaramo* o našim idejama. (Our boss always gives us an opportunity to *discuss* our ideas.)
7. *Razgovarajmo* o planovima za vikend. (Let's *talk* about the plans for the weekend.)
8. Moramo *razgovarati* o problemima koji nas muče. (We need to *talk* about the problems that are bothering us.)
9. Kada *razgovarate* s ljudima, pokušajte biti ljubazni i strpljivi. (When you *speak* with people, try to be kind and patient.)
10. Ne znam s kim bih mogao *razgovarati* o ovom problemu. (I don't know who I could *discuss* this problem with.)